---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section class='prose max-w-none'>
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      Hi, my name is Jungwon Seo, and I am from South Korea.
    </p>
    <p>
      I am currently a Ph.D. candidate, and my thesis has been submitted; I am now awaiting defense. I received my M.S. in Computer Science from the University of Stavanger, with a master's thesis titled <em>Minimum Word Error Rate Training for Speech Separation</em>. I also received my B.S. in Computer Science from Yonsei University.
    </p>
    <p>
      I have worked as a founder or founding engineer at multiple startups, and I also interned at global companies such as Amazon Web Services and Equinor. In addition, I taught Big Data, Machine Learning, and AI courses as a lecturer at the Graduate School of Information, Yonsei University.
    </p>
    <div class='not-prose p-4 rounded-lg bg-base-200 mt-8'>
      <img
        src='/images/jungwon-career-timeline.svg'
        alt='Jungwon Seo career timeline'
        class='w-full h-auto rounded-md'
        loading='lazy'
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
